latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🌎Providing safe, protected produce while decreasing environmental impact is an ongoing and complex challenge for our industry, but one we are focused on solving. Our goal is to be 100% recycle ready by 2025. In celebration of #EarthDay, we want to share our commitment and some promising facts on the future of berry packaging, and how you can help to recover and recycle.

♻️Driscoll’s clamshells contain at least 40% recycled plastic of which 10% comes from recycled clamshells. By 2025, 25% of our PET content will come from recycled clamshells as part of our efforts to close the loop on clamshell packaging.

🍓In 2021 alone, Driscoll’s clamshell to clamshell recycling initiative kept 10.1 million lbs of PET clamshells from going to landfill. These efforts reduced GHG emissions by 5,336 MT CO2 emissions- equivalent to removing 1,133 passenger vehicles from the road annually.

🤝How can you help? Look for the H2R label to learn more about how to recycle our clamshells. Check out @getridwell if there aren’t any PET curbside recycling services in your city or check out @replenysh to find or host a PET recycling event near you.

Tap link in bio to learn more!

latestIgtvVideos.caption:

latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy National Rosé Day!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
"I try to stay positive by reminding myself we — millions of us! — are all in this together." On National Rosé Day, we're taking a moment to celebrate sommeliers whose lives and businesses were affected by the COVID-19 pandemic, and who so graciously partnered with us to create an at-home tasting timeout for you to enjoy. In an effort to bring their talents right into your home, we asked them to share tasting notes, reactions, and wine and food pairing recommendations with our Limited Edition Rosé Berries™. 🥂💕🍃 Tap the link in our bio for more tasting notes and pairing ideas! ⁣

(ad) This Strawberry Lemon Posset with @driscollsberry tastes just like strawberry lemonade. Made with fresh strawberries picked at peak ripeness, this refreshing dessert served inside a lemon is a sweet and tart summer treat.

Comment ‘recipe’ to have this @driscollsberry Strawberry Lemon Posset recipe sent to your DMs 🍓

INGREDIENTS:
5 medium lemons, halved lengthwise
1 ½ cups (8 ounces) Driscoll’s strawberries, hulled and diced
¾ cup (6 ounces) granulated sugar
1 tablespoon cornstarch
1 ½ cups heavy cream
